Stunning Richmond Model in coveted Dominion Valley Country Club  * Gated Community *  RENOVATED 4,847 sq ft Home w/ Designer finishes * Over $140,000 in  renovations in Sept. 2023 * Brand New Hardwood Flooring and Carpet on all 3 Floors * Custom Paint Throughout including Ceiling and Crown Moldings * New Water Heater * Grand Double Level Foyer * Highly desirable Sun-filled two-story Family room with Palladian windows * Floor to Ceiling Stone Fireplace * Separate Living/Dining Room * Sleek Open Kitchen w/ White Cabinets, Center island, Granite countertops, New Backsplash & GE appliances * Breakfast Room * Private Study room * Completely Finished Walk up Basement featuring built-out wet bar w/ dishwasher, wine cooler, and fridge * Can be used as in-law suite w/full bath and separate laundry or recreation room * Amazing Primary Suite boasting a sitting room, large walk-in closet * Luxurious Marbled Primary Bath with oversized shower, Hot Tub, New Vanity and New tile * Princess Suite w/ Renovated full bath * Two secondary bedrooms with Renovated Bath * Two Laundry rooms (main and basement) * Wood deck and Stone Paved flat .26 acres Private backyard * Irrigation System * Large storage room in Basement * World-class amenities: Arnold Palmer Signature Golf Course, renovated Clubhouse, state-of-the-art Sports Pavilion, 5 swimming pools including an indoor pool, tennis & basketball courts, playgrounds, miles of walking/biking trails and two fishing ponds * Award winning schools  * On-site Grocery store, Restaurants, Shops, and Gas station *
